                    </seg> Philh. <metamark function="done" hand="#addressee">⎣</metamark>
                    <metamark function="done" hand="#addressee" spanTo="#pvs_21j_wxb"/>137<anchor type="done" xml:id="pvs_21j_wxb"/>
                </p>
                <p>von meinen Werken erbitte ich <lb/>je 3 Exemplare von <table rows="6" cols="3">
